Ignite Visitor System

 

The Ignite Visitor System is comprised of a web-based scheduling app, iPad app, and name badge printer
that allows Ignite staff to add members and visitors to check-in with a touchless experience.

Add a Member

Back to top

 

1.       Go to https://ignitevisitorsystem.github.io/

2.       Click on Schedule Visitor

3.       Completely fill-out ALL fields then Click on Schedule Visitor

4.       Create email to visitor

a.       Click link: Click here to create email to guest

b.      Edit email to personalize

c.       Send email (see below image)

 

View/Update Member

Back to top

1.       Go to https://ignitevisitorsystem.github.io/?all=yes

2.       Find member & click on the click here link (See image below)

3.       Update data: Edit data fields then click Update Visit button (see #1 in image below)

4.       Make member active/in-active: Click on link below Status: (see #2 un image below)

Check-In Using iPad App

Back to top

1.       First-time user that did not get email from with link to QR code

a.       Tap Here to Check-In button

b.      Complete all fields

c.       Tap Submit button

d.      Take photo of QR code for subsequent check-ins

e.      Tap Check-In button

2.       Subsequent Visits or users that received an email with link to QR code

a.       Scan QR Code (Preferred Method). Retrieve name badge from printer
OR

b.      Tap Here to Check-In button

                                                               i.      Enter last name

                                                             ii.      Tap [Return] key to retrieve record

                                                            iii.      Tap Select button

                                                           iv.      Tap Tap Here to Check-In button

                                                             v.      Retrieve name badge from printer

Reports

Back to top

1)    Check-in report by date: ignitevisitorsystem.github.io/?all=today

2)    Members

a.    Active members: ignitevisitorsystem.github.io/?all=yes

b.    In-Active members ignitevisitorsystem.github.io/?all=no
